<blockquote>
<h1 id="toc1"><span>SITE DIRECTOR'S NOTICE:</span></h1>
<p><strong>Due to the graphic details described below, information pertaining to SCP-2610 is on a need-to-know basis, and is currently restricted to Level 3/2610 personnel only.</strong></p>
<h2 id="toc2"><span>Discretion is advised.</span></h2>
